title: Foul Play (1978) (Goldie Hawn, Chevy Chase, Dudley Moore)
description:
FOUL PLAY - 1978

IMDb Rating: 6.5
http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0077578/

  Goldie Hawn plays Gloria, a librarian "ready to take a chance again," who ends up the target of an assassination ring. Chevy Chase is Tony, the cop assigned to protect Gloria. Dudley Moore is a surprisingly kinky symphony conductor. There are grandmothers playing Scrabble with expletives, Burgess Meredith's snake Esme, and an old Japanese couple in the back of the careening limo. What more can I say?
  This is great little feel good screwball comedy from the 70's.
